A cyberpunk cityscape at night where streams of glowing data packets flow like rivers between towering server monoliths, each packet color-coded in neon blues, purples, and oranges representing different data types being imported and channeled through luminous conduits. In the foreground, a lone developer figure in a hooded jacket stands on a platform, orchestrating the data streams with holographic gesture controls, routing information from massive floating crystalline structures labeled only by distinct geometric symbols into a central nexus point. The atmosphere is hazy with digital fog, rain streaking through laser grid lines, and reflections shimmering on wet metallic surfaces below.
